ctrl a - go to the beginner of the line
ctrl e - go to the end  of the line
ctrl u - delete everything from the cursor point to the beginner of the line
ctrl k - delete everything from the cursor to the end of the line.


ctrl w - delete word backward
alt d - delete word forward
ctrl y - redo
alt . - redo the previous argument from the last command
!$ - redo the previous argument from the last command
!! - add the last command; ex: "sudo !!"

